Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Magsaysay, in the Province of Isabela, to the Municipality of Delfin Albano
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 291
An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Magsaysay, in the Province of Isabela, to the Municipality of Delfin Albano
Section 1. The Municipality of Magsaysay, in the Province of Isabela, shall hereafter be known as the Municipality of Delfin Albano.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: November 14, 1982
